item.title: CVE-2023-44283|2024-08-14T18:49:25.331Z -- dell -- supportassist%20for%20home%20pcs
item.description: In Dell SupportAssist for Home PCs (between v3.0 and v3.14.1) and SupportAssist for Business PCs (between v3.0 and v3.4.1), a security concern has been identified, impacting locally authenticated users on their respective PCs. This issue may potentially enable privilege escalation and the execution of arbitrary code, in the Windows system context, and confined to that specific local PC.
